title: Overcoming Supply Chain Issues on a Home Reno
description: Architects Jordan Rogove and Wayne Norbeck, co-founders of DXA studio, join Mansion Global reporter Leslie Hendrickson in a discussion of the rising costs of home construction and how to navigate ongoing supply chain issues.
